block notific8DemoTitle
  h1 notific8 demo
p notific8 is a highly customizable JavaScript notification plug-in. It comes with multiple themes built in. The Sass files can be included in a project for easy customizations.
p Use the fields below to test the different options for the plug-in.
p
  | To see the
  i  onInit(data)
  | ,
  i  onCreate(notification, data)
  | , and
  i  onClose(notification, data)
  |  actions functioning, open your browser's developer tools' console view.

hr

fieldset
  legend Notification Queue
  p
    input#notific8Queue(type='checkbox', name='notific8Queue', value='1')
    label(for='notific8Queue')  Queue notifications
  div
    em Note: queuing is set for the plug-in settings and not passed in as an option on the notification. It will only be process in the first notification call.
  .input-field
    label(for='notific8QueueName') Notification Name
    input#notific8QueueName(type='text', name='notific8QueueName', size='50', maxlength='50')
  div
    em The notification name is only used when notifications are queued. If no name is passed in, a unique name is generated. The notification name is returned when a notification is created or queued.
br

block upperConfig

.input-field
  label(for='notific8Text') Notification text
  input#notific8Text(type='text', name='notific8Text', size='50', maxlength='300', value='Test notific8 notification')

p
  input#notific8Sticky(type='checkbox', name='notific8Sticky')
  label(for='notific8Sticky')  Sticky (if checked, setting life below will be ignored)
br

.input-field
  select#notific8Life(name='notific8Life')
    option(value='1000') 1 second
    option(value='5000') 5 seconds
    option(value='10000', selected='selected') 10 seconds (default)
    option(value='25000') 25 seconds
    option(value='60000') 60 seconds
  label(for='notific8Life') Life

.input-field
  label(for='notific8Heading') Heading (optional)
  input#notific8Heading(type='text', name='notific8Heading', size='50', maxlength='50')
  br
div
